    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"YHaMYdptLi3fXfVH\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Bombard</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl00_LabelName\">As a full action, you can make a ranged attack that knocks enemies back. Targets you hit are knocked back 5 feet from you. If you use a weapon with the explode special property, all targets that fail their saving throws are instead knocked back 5 feet from the center of the explosion. An enemy that you critically hit or that rolls a natural 1 on its saving throw is also knocked prone. You canâ€™t make an impactful attack with an automatic weapon, but you can use this ability with a weapon that has the blast special property.</span></p>",
